          <div class="section-title">
            <h2>Happy Story</h2>
          </div>
          <p>Happy Bar & Grill is a chain of casual restaurants, with a 27-year history, starting on the eve of Christmas 1994, and as of today there are already 23 Happy Bar & Grill restaurants in major cities and the national road network in the country, with service standards imposed and interior.
            The chain is also represented abroad with 3 restaurants in Spain, Barcelona. In January 2020 we are opening our first restaurant in London at the iconic Piccadilly Circus.
            
            Thanks to the combination of the quality of the food, high standard of service and added value such as pleasure and overall atmosphere.</p>
          <p> In Bulgaria, the Happy Bar & Grill brand is the strongest in its class and for 13 consecutive years it has won the Favorite Brand award and for the fifteenth consecutive year it has won the award of the Association of Hoteliers and Restaurateurs in Bulgaria for "Most Successful Restaurant Chain".</p>
        </div>
